## 2026-04-03 - ColorPicker token swatch panel strips alpha from 8-char hex colors
- Fixed two bugs in `colorTokens` useMemo at `ColorPicker.tsx:355`: (1) changed `v.slice(0, 7)` to `v` for both `hex` and `cssColor` fields so `#RRGGBBAA` values are preserved; (2) added `setAlpha(parseAlpha(t.hex))` in the token swatch click handler so selecting an 8-char hex token also applies its alpha, matching the existing recent-colors click handler pattern.
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/ColorPicker.tsx` ~L355, ~L939
- **Learnings for future iterations:**

